room_title: Escape room "Sherlock Holmes Final Case" by Race to Escape in Tampa
room_address: 2435 US Highway 19 N Suite 101 Holiday, FL 34691
room_description: Sherlock Holmes has mysteriously disappeared during the largest case he has ever tried to crack. A serial killer is still on the loose on the London streets and new victims continue to show up every night. You are tasked to find Sherlock Holmes' clue he left behind in his office and find the murderer before he strikes again!
